#![allow(unnamed_duplicate_typed_args)]
# SimpleOS Glass Window Manager — x86_64 Render Primitives + Theme + Chrome
#
# Extracted from wm_entry.spl. Contains:
#   - Extern FFI declarations (rendering + layout)
#   - pack / pack8 helpers
#   - Screen dimensions, theme token constants, layout constants
#   - Easing functions (bounce_offset, ease_out_cubic, ease_in_cubic, lerp, etc.)
#   - Dock icon color constants
#   - Rendering primitive helpers (fill, blend, blur, grad_h/v, etc.)
#   - Text rendering helpers (draw_label, draw_label_shadow, etc.)
#   - Layout engine helpers and constants
#   - Theme-aware color getters (surface, elevated, accent, text_c, etc.)
#   - WM Chrome stylesheet helpers (chrome_draw_surface, chrome_draw_menu_item, etc.)
#
# No module-level var state — all functions are pure or stateless wrappers.

# === Extern FFI declarations ===
